A boat with about 200 people on board has caught fire at Hartbeespoort dam, North West on Satuday &#8211; 4 people dead so far.Paramedics on scene say it was one of the party boats that caught fire the cause is still unknown.One person was burnt to death in the bathroom and 3 people have drowned.When the boat caught fire smaller boats in the area went closer to help, but were overloaded and capsized.Paramedics say there are still busy treating many people and they are trying to establish how many are missing.-TNA Reporter